{"id":20055,"date":"2014-11-30T13:59:53","date_gmt":"2014-11-30T09:59:53","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/www.dailyhadithonline.com\/?p=20055"},"modified":"2019-04-30T10:21:50","modified_gmt":"2019-04-30T06:21:50","slug":"love-muhammad-more-than-anything","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/11\/30\/love-muhammad-more-than-anything\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Muhammad: A man who loves the Prophet more than anything"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Aisha reported: A man came to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and he said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, by Allah, I love you more than myself, more than my family and wealth. You are more beloved to me than my children. I would be in my house and remember you until I cannot wait to see you. When I remember my death and your death, I know you will enter Paradise with the status of the prophets, but if I enter Paradise I am afraid I will not see you.\u201d The Prophet did not answer him with anything until Gabriel, upon him be peace, was sent with this verse, \u201c<strong>Whoever obeys Allah and the messenger, they will be with those whom Allah has blessed among the prophets, the truthful, the martyrs, and the righteous<\/strong>.\u201d (4:69)<\/p>\n<p>Source: al-Mu&#8217;jam al-S\u0323aghi\u0304r 52<\/p>\n<p>Grade: <strong><em>Sahih li ghayrihi<\/em><\/strong> (authentic due to external evidence) according to Ahmad Shakir<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u062a\u0652 \u062c\u064e\u0627\u0621\u064e \u0631\u064e\u062c\u064f\u0644\u064c \u0625\u0650\u0644\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0641\u064e\u0642\u064e\u0627\u06